article_title: 10 Worst Places to Live for Obamacare
article_text:
Colorado Mountain Resort Region: $483

This list represents the 10 most expensive regions for insurance based on monthly premiums. It was compiled using monthly silver premiums, or the standard plan, for a 40-year-old individual. The ranking is based on rates listed in federal and state insurance marketplaces and data compiled by the Kaiser Family Foundation. Read more on this at The Fiscal Times.
